1. This folder contains all R scripts for the main analysis for the study titled "Global prevalence of preserved ratio impaired spirometry and restrictive spirometry pattern in the general population: a systematic review and meta-analysis".
2. The main meta-analysis only includes studies which defined PRISm and/or RSP using the Global Initiative for Chronic Obstructive Lung Disease (GOLD) criteria.
3. Please ensure that data_prevalence.csv file is in the working directory.
